k. I remain deeply interested in contributing to [Journal Name] and am committed to submitting a revised version that meets your high expectations.\n\nThank you again for your consideration and for the constructive feedback provided. I look forward to the possibility of resubmitting this work in the near future.\n\nSincerely,\n\n[Your Full Name]  \n[Your Title/Position]  \n[Your Institution/Organization]  \n[Your Contact Information]\n",
