      "response": "Here is a complete, self-contained HTML file. It uses semantic tags (`header`, `main`, `article`, `footer`) and includes an embedded `<style>` block to handle the CSS.\n\nThe timeline expands the narrative to include the birth of the protagonist, the marriage, and the post-wedding life, using fictional dates to create a cohesive story arc.\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>The Journey of Elara Vance</title>\n    <style>\n        /* General Reset and Typography */\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: #f4f4f9;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Layout Container */\n        .container {\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        /* Header Styling */\n        header {\n            background-color: #2c3e50;\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #e67e22;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-style: italic;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        /* Main Timeline Structure */\n        main {\n            position: relative;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        /* The Vertical Line */\n        main::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            left: 50%;\n            width: 4px;\n            background: #bdc3c7;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n        }\n\n        /* Individual Timeline Items */\n        .timeline-item {\n         