ements, job application tracking, and industry-specific news feeds that blend personal branding with professional development. This diverse array of specialized tools ensures that social media remains a dynamic and adaptable infrastructure for human interaction, constantly evolving to meet the shifting demands of a hyper-connected world.\n",
