      "s_gold": "According to the provided text, the growth in demand for fruit snacks and nuts in Russia can be attributed to several factors. Firstly, there has been a shift in consumer preferences towards healthier snacking options, and fruit snacks and nuts are perceived as healthier alternatives to traditional confectionery and bakery items. Additionally, manufacturers and retailers have improved their offer of packaged fruit snacks and nuts by launching a variety of products in different packaging formats and price segments, which has helped to drive demand. Furthermore, the economic recovery and growing consumer expenditure on food in Russia have also contributed to the increased demand for sweet and savoury snacks, including fruit snacks and nuts.",
