      "u_instruction": "Create a brochure using a vibrant, chaotic design with excessive emojis, colorful graphics, and enthusiastic language to maximize visual excitement and engagement.",
      "s_gold": "**The 2023 School Event**\n\nA Celebration of Learning!\n\nTheme: \"The Future of Education\"\n\nDate: Saturday, February 18, 2023\n\nTime: 10am - 4pm\n\nLocation: [School name]\n\n[Image of a group of students laughing and learning together]\n\nThe 2023 School Event is a free event for all students, parents, and teachers. It will feature a variety of activities and speakers on the topic of education. The event will be a great opportunity to learn about new and innovative educational ideas, network with other educators, and support the school.\n\n[Image of a teacher giving a presentation]\n\nKeynote Speakers:\n\n* Dr. Jane Doe, Education Professor at [University name]\n* Mr. John Smith, Principal at [School name]\n* Ms. Sara Jones, Parent and Community Activist\n\n[Image of a doctor giving a presentation]\n\nFeatured Activities:\n\n* Interactive workshops on topics such as STEM education, STEAM education, and project-based learning\n* Panel discussions on the future of education\n* A student showcase of creative projects\n* A keynote address by Dr. Jane Doe\n\n[Image of a group of students working on a project together]\n\nRegistration:\n\nRegistration is free for all students, parents, and teachers. To register, please visit [website address].\n\n[Image of a website with a registration form]\n\nWe hope to see you there!\n\n[Image of a group of students smiling and waving]",
      "u_gold": "Title: Join us for a Fun-Filled School Event!\nSubtitle: Explore the World of [Theme] with Exciting Performances, Engaging Workshops, and Delicious Food!\nDear [Name],\nWe are thrilled to invite you to our upcoming school event, [Event Name], happening on [Date] at [Location]! This exciting event promises to be an unforgettable experience, filled with fun, learning, and exposure to new ideas.\nTheme: [Theme]\nLocation: [Location]\nDate: [Date]\nTime: [Time]\nSpeakers/Performers: [List of speakers or performers]\nAttn: All attendees must register in advance to ensure a smooth and enjoyable experience. Please visit our website or contact us for more information on registration fees and payment details.\nHighlights:\n\ud83c\udf1f Exciting performances by [List of performers]\n\ud83c\udfa8 Engaging workshops on [List of workshops]\n\ud83c\udf7d\ufe0f Delicious food and drinks from around the world!\n\ud83d\udcda Interactive activities and games to learn something new every hour!\n\ud83d\udde3\ufe0f Amazing keynote speakers sharing their insights and experiences on [Themed topic]\n\ud83c\udfa8 Spectacular visuals and multimedia presentations to enhance your learning experience\n\ud83d\udc65 Networking opportunities with like-minded individuals from diverse backgrounds and industries!\nDon't miss out on this incredible opportunity to expand your knowledge, broaden your horizons, and make new connections! Mark your calendars and join us for an unforgettable day of fun, learning, and growth!\nCall to Action:\nVisit our website or contact us to register and secure your spot today! Limited spots available, so don't wait!\nWe look forward to seeing you there!\nBest regards,\nThe [School/Organization] Team\n\nEye-catching Images and Graphics:\n\ud83c\udf1f Sparkly balloons and streamers in the event's theme color\n\ud83c\udfa8 Doodles and illustrations of the event's speakers and performers\n\ud83c\udf7d\ufe0f Pictures of delicious food and drinks from around the world\n\ud83d\udcda Symbols of learning, such as books, pens, and notebooks\n\ud83d\udde3\ufe0f Images of a speaker podium or a stage for the keynote speakers\n\ud83c\udfa8 Vibrant, colorful graphics featuring the event's theme and activities\n\ud83d\udc65 Silhouettes or avatars of attendees networking and connecting with each other.",
      "response": "Here are two distinct brochure concepts designed to meet your specific requirements.\n\n### Option 1: The Clean & Minimalist Brochure\n**Theme:** \"Essence of Simplicity\"\n**Design Philosophy:** White space, sans-serif typography, monochromatic palette, and high-contrast photography.\n\n---\n\n**[FRONT COVER]**\n*(Visual: A single, high-resolution black-and-white photo of a minimalist landscape or abstract geometric shape centered on a pure white background.)*\n\n**HEADLINE:**\n# CLARITY IN EVERY DETAIL\n**Sub-headline:** Experience the power of simplicity.\n\n---\n\n**[INSIDE PAGE 1: The Philosophy]**\n*(Visual: A subtle, low-opacity line drawing of a house or tree in the corner.)*\n\n**THE VISION**\nIn a world of noise, we choose silence. Our approach strips away the unnecessary to reveal what truly matters. We believe that design is not about adding more, but about removing the rest.\n\n*   **Less is More:** Every element serves a purpose.\n*   **Timeless:** Styles that never go out of fashion.\n*   **Focus:** Clear paths to your goals.\n\n---\n\n**[INSIDE PAGE 2: Our Services]**\n*(Visual: Three simple, outlined icons arranged horizontally: a Pen, a Compass, and a Shield.)*\n\n**WHAT WE OFFER**\n\n*   **Strategic Planning**\n    Mapping your journey with precision and foresight.\n    > *\"We don't just plan; we predict.\"*\n\n*   **Creative Direction**\n    Guiding your brand with a steady, clear hand.\n    > *\"Vision made visible.\"*\n\n*   **Execution**\n    Bringing ideas to life with flawless craftsmanship.\n    > *\"Perfection in every pixel.\"*\n\n---\n\n**[BACK COVER]**\n*(Visual: A solid black background with a single white contact line in the center.)*\n\n**GET IN TOUCH**\nReady to simplify your world?\n\n\ud83d\udce7 hello@minimalist.co\n\ud83d\udccd 123 Quiet Lane, Design District\n\ud83c\udf10 www.minimalist.co\n\n*\u00a9 2023 Minimalist Co. All rights reserved.*\n\n***\n\n### Option 2: The Vibrant & Chaotic Brochure\n**Theme:** \"EXPLOSION OF COLOR!\"\n**Design Philosophy:** Clashing gradients, overlapping text, dynamic angles, excessive emojis, and high-energy typography.\n\n---\n\n**[FRONT COVER]**\n*(Visual: A background of swirling neon pink, electric blue, and lime green gradients. Overlaid are 5-6 different fonts, some tilted at 45 degrees, some bold, some outlined.)*\n\n**HEADLINE:**\n# \ud83d\ude80 WELCOME TO THE MADNESS! \ud83c\udf89\n**Sub-headline:** Get ready to PARTY, CREATE, and CONQUER! \ud83d\udca5\u2728\n\n**BANNER:**\n\ud83c\udf08 **COLOR IS KING!** \ud83d\udc51\n\ud83d\udd25 **ENERGY IS EVERYTHING!** \u26a1\n\n---\n\n**[INSIDE PAGE 1: The Vibe]**\n*(Visual: A collage of 4 tiny, bright photos: a dancing cat \ud83d\udc31, a rocket ship \ud83d\ude80, a rainbow \ud83c\udf08, and a firework \ud83d\udca5.)*\n\n**THE VIBES ARE OFF THE CHARTS! \ud83d\udcc8**\nWhy settle for boring when you can be BOLD? \ud83e\udd29 We bring the chaos, the color, and the pure joy to your brand!\n\n*   **\ud83c\udfa8 Creative Chaos:** We mix colors until they POP!\n*   **\ud83d\ude80 Speed & Power:** Fast, furious, and fun!\n*   **\ud83e\udd2a Unapologetic Style:** Be different! Be loud! Be YOU!\n\n**QUOTE:**\n\"Life is short. Make it colorful! \ud83c\udf1f\ud83c\udf1f\ud83c\udf1f\"\n\n---\n\n**[INSIDE PAGE 2: The Services]**\n*(Visual: Each service is in a different colored box with a wavy border.)*\n\n**OUR SUPER POWERS! \ud83d\udcaa**\n\n*   **\ud83c\udfa8 Design Magic**\n    We turn your ideas into art that screams!\n    *   Logos that laugh! \ud83d\ude02\n    *   Posters that party! \ud83e\udd73\n    *   Websites that zoom! \ud83c\udfce\ufe0f\n\n*   **\ud83d\udce2 Marketing Mayhem**\n    Get noticed by the whole world! \ud83c\udf0d\n    *   Social media that spins! \ud83d\udd04\n    *   Ads that explode! \ud83d\udca3\n    *   Campaigns that cheer! \ud83d\udce3\n\n*   **\ud83e\udd1d Team Hype**\n    We work hard, we play hard, we win hard! \ud83c\udfc6\n    *   Collaboration that clicks! \ud83d\udd17\n    *   Support",
