      "s_gold": "Hello Jase! How may I assist you today? \ud83d\ude0a As a helpful, respectful, and honest assistant, I'm here to provide accurate and engaging content tailored to your needs. Please feel free to ask any questions, and I'll do my best to provide a helpful response. \ud83e\udd14\n\n Based on the biography you provided, I understand that you are an award-winning social media director, creative producer, and public relations manager with extensive experience in communications, advertising, tourism, and government relations. You have served in various leadership roles, including President of the Public Relations Association of Mississippi \u2013 Beach Chapter and Past-President of the Gulfport Gridiron Club. You are also a 2022 One Coast Top 10 Under 40 recipient, CYP \u201cMVP\u201d award recipient, and a graduate of the Gulf Coast Business Council Masters Leadership Program.\n\nCurrently, you serve as the spokesperson for the City of Gulfport, overseeing all public relations, internal and external communications, branding, and marketing for the state's second-largest city. You have also worked in leadership roles in the advertising and marketing industry and as the Director of Communications & Engagement for Coastal Mississippi.\n\nPlease let me know if there's anything specific you'd like to discuss or inquire about. I'm here to help! \ud83d\ude0a",
