      "s_gold": "Title: Quiz Game Scoring Policy\n\nObjective: To create a fair, enjoyable, and challenging quiz game experience for players by implementing an effective scoring policy.\n\n1. Total Questions and Answer Choices:\n   The quiz game comprises 10 questions, each having 3 possible answer choices (A, B, and C).\n\n2. Scoring Rules:\n   a. Correct Answer: For every correct answer, the player earns 10 points. \n      Total possible points for a perfect game: 100 points.\n   b. Incorrect Answer: For each incorrect answer or skipped question, the player receives 0 points.\n   c. Time Bonus: If players answer a question quickly, they receive bonus points based on their speed:\n         - Answer within 5 seconds: +3 bonus points\n         - Answer within 10 seconds: +2 bonus points\n         - Answer within 15 seconds: +1 bonus point\n\n3. Scoring Display:\n   After each question, the player will be shown their current score, including the points earned from the latest question and any relevant time bonus points.\n\n4. Final Score Breakdown:\n   At the end of the game, players will see the following breakdown for their total score:\n      - Points for correct answers\n      - Points from time bonuses\n      - Total score (sum of correct answer points and time bonuses)\n\n5. Difficulty Levels and Scaling:\n   To customize the game experience, the quiz can offer different difficulty levels (e.g., Easy, Medium, and Hard). The scoring policy will be scaled accordingly for each level:\n      - Easy: Correct Answer = 5 points, Time Bonus remains the same\n      - Medium: Correct Answer = 10 points, Time Bonus remains the same\n      - Hard: Correct Answer = 15 points, Time Bonus remains the same\n\n6. Ranking and Leaderboard System:\n   Players' performance in the game will be ranked based on their total scores and displayed on a leaderboard. The leaderboard will be updated regularly to reflect the current top-ranked players.\n\n7. Tiebreakers for the Ranking:\n   In the event of a tie, players' rankings will be determined by the following factors, in order:\n      - Number of correct answers\n      - Total time bonus points\n      - Fastest completion time for the whole quiz\n\nImplementing this scoring policy will ensure a fun and engaging experience for players while providing an accurate representation of their skills and knowledge.",
