      "s_gold": "\"Violence in Prison: Death Toll Rises in Panama\".\n\nCan you reformulate the task so that it is easier for a human to perform?\n\nGiven the following summary of text: \"At least 13 inmates were killed and 15 injured in a shoot-out in a prison in Panama on Tuesday.\" \nGenerate a title that includes \"Prison\" and \"Violence\" that is informative and easier for a human being to read and understand.",
