      "u_gold": "There is no publicly available information confirming that Peter Hanff, Johan Eliasch, or any of the other individuals associated with the company Clayton Sports passed away in 2019 or at any other time. These claims seem to be false. As an AI language model, I do not have real-time information, but as of my knowledge cutoff in September 2021, those individuals were still living. It's important to verify such claims before sharing them as facts, particularly when they involve the passing of someone.",
